CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780862761
OL,3,CNHS trust settles for #28m with family
OL,4,Cof brain-damaged girl
OL,6,FThe family of a girl who suffered
OL,7,Fbrain damage at birth has been awarded
OL,8,F#28 million in an out-of-court
OL,9,Fsettlement after an NHS trust admitted
OL,10,Fnegligence.
OL,12,FBarking, Havering and Redbridge
OL,13,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Trust
OL,14,Facknowledged an error in the delivery
OL,15,Fof the girl who suffered severe
OL,16,Fhypoxia-ischaemia.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780862761
OL,3,CNHS trust settles for #28m with family
OL,4,Cof brain-damaged girl
OL,6,FLawyers for the family, who brought
OL,7,Flegal action at the High Court, said
OL,8,Fthe girl, who is now of primary school
OL,9,Fage, will need lifelong care to
OL,10,Falleviate her cognitive and language
OL,11,Fimpairments and will need constant
OL,12,Fsupervision as she has no danger
OL,13,Fawareness and is over-friendly with
OL,14,Fstrangers.
OL,16,FShe also has epilepsy with
OL,17,Funpredictable seizures and is
OL,18,Fpredicted to lose mobility throughout
OL,19,Fher life, the expectancy of which is
OL,20,Faround 83 years.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780862761
OL,3,CNHS trust settles for #28m with family
OL,4,Cof brain-damaged girl
OL,6,FDespite her difficulties, she is
OL,7,Ffinding joy through music therapy and
OL,8,Fis particularly fond of the piano and
OL,9,Fdrums, which has boosted her
OL,10,Fconfidence and communication
OL,11,Fabilities, the lawyers said.
OL,13,FHer mother said: "My daughter is
OL,14,Fthriving and doing well but it's
OL,15,Fimpossible for me to forget that I was
OL,16,Frobbed of the precious experience of
OL,17,Fmost mothers giving birth by the
OL,18,Fhorror of what happened to us.
OL,26,@uD@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780862761
OL,3,CNHS trust settles for #28m with family
OL,4,Cof brain-damaged girl
OL,6,F"Seven years on, I'm still deeply
OL,7,Faffected by seeing the hospital's name
OL,8,Fcrop up in the press regarding
OL,9,Ftragedies for other families and their
OL,10,Fbabies.
OL,12,F"This is despite the repeated promises
OL,13,Fof the Government and endless reviews
OL,14,Finto maternity safety. Surely someone
OL,15,Fmust take the bull by the horns and
OL,16,Ftake action to change things."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780862761
OL,3,CNHS trust settles for #28m with family
OL,4,Cof brain-damaged girl
OL,6,FThe order, approved by Deputy Judge
OL,7,FChristopher Kennedy, says the trust
OL,8,Fmust pay a lump sum of #8 million,
OL,9,Ffollowed by an annual sum of #225,000
OL,10,Ffor 10 years, with further annual
OL,11,Fpayments of #335,000 after that.
OL,13,FHealth Secretary James Murray said on
OL,14,FMonday that recommendations for NHS
OL,15,Fmaternity services must not sit "on
OL,16,Fshelves" and that the reforms must be
OL,17,F"comprehensive".
OL,26,@wD@aOUxD@HO]yD@AOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780862761
OL,3,CNHS trust settles for #28m with family
OL,4,Cof brain-damaged girl
OL,6,FHe told the BBC he has been meeting
OL,7,Ffamilies whose babies died, which
OL,8,F"brings it home in the strongest
OL,9,Fpossible sense, how human and how
OL,10,Fdevastating this can be, and how
OL,11,Fimportant it is that we change".
OL,13,FJane Weakley from Fieldfisher, who
OL,14,Frepresented the family in the
OL,15,Fnegligence claim, said: "Too many
OL,16,Ftimes the medical negligence team at
OL,17,FFieldfisher takes on cases where the
OL,18,Fsame terrible mistakes are repeated,
OL,19,Fbringing untold tragedy.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@_O]wD@YOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780862761
OL,3,CNHS trust settles for #28m with family
OL,4,Cof brain-damaged girl
OL,6,F'We fully support the NHS and appeal
OL,7,Fto the Government to please fulfil
OL,8,Ftheir promise to make maternity care
OL,9,Fsafe for mothers and babies."
OL,11,FNic Kane, chief nurse at Barking,
OL,12,FHavering and Redbridge University
OL,13,FHospitals NHS Trust, said: "We're
OL,14,Fextremely sorry the care this child
OL,15,Fand their family experienced was not
OL,16,Fgood enough.
OL,26,@qD@]O]uD@\OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780862761
OL,3,CNHS trust settles for #28m with family
OL,4,Cof brain-damaged girl
OL,6,F"We'd like to reassure them, and all
OL,7,Four expectant mothers, that since this
OL,8,Fbirth in 2019, we've learned lessons,
OL,9,Fmade significant changes, and our
OL,10,Fmaternity department has been rated
OL,11,Fgood by the Care Quality Commission.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780862761
OL,3,CNHS trust settles for #28m with family
OL,4,Cof brain-damaged girl
OL,6,F"The improvements include more
OL,7,Fobstetric and midwifery staff in
OL,8,Ftriage to ensure women are reviewed
OL,9,Fand concerns escalated quicker, more
OL,10,Frobust training on CTG monitoring `
OL,11,Fused to monitor the baby's heart rate
OL,12,Fand mother's contractions ` and we are
OL,13,Fpart of a national programme, run by
OL,14,Fthe Royal College of Obstetricians and
OL,15,FGynaecologists, which focuses on
OL,16,Freducing the risk of avoidable harm in
OL,17,Fchildbirth."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
